childMarkdownRemark.rawMarkdownBody: __Oumayma__ is from Oujda, Morocco where she works as a __full stack engineer__ at Novelis Consulting. She has 1.5 years experience as a __JavaEE/React software engineer__ with a focus on APIs and micro-services, recently, she took the plunge on __mobile development__ with __react-native__ and __kotlin__. In her spare time she is an avid traveler, lover of gourmet cooking and tries her best to live life to the fullest.
